        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline__event timeline__eventtype-mandir">
          <div class="timeline__event-date">
              374 VNS
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__event-title text-center">Elephant cave in Khandgiri, Orissa</div>
          
          <!-- ASPECT RATIO 16:9, DIMENSION OF IMAGES SHOULD BE 320X180 -->
          <img class="timeline__event-image" src="/static/images/timeline/udaygirikhandagiri.jpg" alt="Elephant cave in Khandgiri, Orissa"/>
          
          <!-- DESCRIPTION SHOULD BE LESS THAN 270 CHARACTERS -->
          <div class="timeline__event-descr">An inscription about Kharavela a devout Jain still exists in Khandagiri, Orissa. It is written that Kharavela defeated Pushyamitra and took the statue of Rishabhdev famously known as Kalinga Jin. This statue was built by Shrenik Maharaja and made auspicious by Sudharma Swami in Kumaragiri.</div>
          
          <div class="timeline__event-actions">
            <a 
              class="timeline__event-action" 
