        <div class="timeline__event timeline__eventtype-gyan">
          <div class="timeline__event-date">
              375 VNS
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__event-title text-center">2nd Agam Vachna</div>
          
          <!-- ASPECT RATIO 16:9, DIMENSION OF IMAGES SHOULD BE 320X180 -->
          <img class="timeline__event-image" src="/static/images/timeline/AgamVachna2.jpg" alt="2nd Agam Vachna"/>
          
          <!-- DESCRIPTION SHOULD BE LESS THAN 270 CHARACTERS -->
          <div class="timeline__event-descr">On Kumaragiri, Kalingaraj Kharavel convened the 2nd Agam Vachna Conference under the guidance of Arya Susthitsuri and Supratibaddhsuuri. In this Arya Belissah composed ‘Angavidya’, Sri Swati composed ‘Tattvaratha’ and Mr. Shyamacharya composed ‘Pragyapana’ sutra.</div>
          
          <div class="timeline__event-actions">
            <a 
              class="timeline__event-action" 
              href="https://www.historyofjainism.com/timeline/jain-kings#h.s4unrdvny5m4" 
