                Read More
            </a>
          </div>
          
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline__event timeline__eventtype-gyan">
          <div class="timeline__event-date">
              580* VNS
          </div>
          <div class="timeline__event-title text-center">3rd Agam Vachna</div>
          
          <!-- ASPECT RATIO 16:9, DIMENSION OF IMAGES SHOULD BE 320X180 -->
          <img class="timeline__event-image" src="/static/images/timeline/mandsaur.jpg" alt="3rd Agam Vachna"/>
          
          <!-- DESCRIPTION SHOULD BE LESS THAN 270 CHARACTERS -->
          <div class="timeline__event-descr">During the 12-year drought period, most Sadhus including Vajraswami left for heaven. The 10th Purv was also lost. Under the leadership of Vajrasensuuri, Nandilasuri and Rakshitsuri ji, 3rd agam vachna was held and after a few years, the Shramana Sangha was arranged in four clans.</div>
          
          <div class="timeline__event-actions">
            <a 
              class="timeline__event-action" 
